column2: SELECT s.mjd, s.plate, s.fiberID, s.z as z, g.oii_#_flux, g.oii_#_eqw, g.oii_#_flux, g.oii_#_eqw, g.neiii_#_flux, g.neiii_#_eqw, p.dered_g as g_color, p.dered_z as z_color, p.dered_r as r_color, w.w1mpro as w1, w.w2mpro as w2, w.w3mpro as w3 FROM WISE_xmatch AS x JOIN WISE_allsky AS w ON x.wise_cntr = w.cntr JOIN (SELECT * FROM SpecPhotoAll WHERE SpecPhotoAll.nChild = # AND SpecPhotoAll.dered_g > # AND SpecPhotoAll.dered_z > # AND SpecPhotoAll.dered_r > #) AS p ON x.sdss_objid = p.objid JOIN (SELECT * FROM SpecObjAll WHERE SpecObjAll.z < # AND SpecObjAll.snmedian_g > # AND SpecObjAll.snmedian_r > #) AS s ON s.specobjid = p.specobjid WHERE (s.class = # or s.class = #) ORDER BY s.z DESC
